程序包 cn.qfys521.string

类 SuppressWarningsStrings

java.lang.Object
cn.qfys521.string.SuppressWarningsStrings
public class SuppressWarningsStrings extends Object
Provides a collection of constant strings representing common suppression annotations used in Java code. These annotations can be applied to classes, methods, or fields to suppress specific types of compiler warnings.
